        <form action="/contact"  accept-charset="UTF-8" method="post" id="contact-mail-page">
<div><h3>Contact Information</h3>
<p>If you need to contact WHFR.FM, you can leave a message using the contact form below.</p>
<h4>Mailing Address</h4>
<p>WHFR 89.3FM / HFCC<br />
5101 Evergreen Rd.<br />
Dearborn, MI 48128<br />
USA</p>
<h4>Email Address</h4>
<p>whfr@hfcc.edu</p>
<h4>Request Hotlines</h4>
<ul>
<li>800-585-HFCC x9676</li>
<li>313-845-9676</li>
<li>313-317-4034 (fax)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Staff Directory</h3>
<p>Need to contact a specific staff member? If so, check out the <a href="/about/staff">staff directory</a>.</p>
<h3>Send Us Music</h3>
<p>If you want to send WHFR.FM music for possible airtime, <a href="/about/send-music">please view this page</a> for information on how to send your tape, record, or CD to the station.</p>

